    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone needing dependable transportation on a budget. The engine and transmission are fully functional, though you should expect some minor fluid seepage and typical wear consistent with its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading, while the interior shows clear signs of use, including some wear on the upholstery. It has been regularly maintained, but it will likely require some minor suspension work and a tune-up in the near future to keep it running at its best.",
