    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This specimen exhibits showroom-caliber aesthetics and mechanical integrity, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, confirms its status as a premier example of its class. This is a definitive acquisition for those who demand uncompromising quality and a vehicle in peerless condition.",
      "price": 46500.0,
