    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to drive away in your dream car? This absolute beauty is in stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered and kept in truly flawless shape, so you\u2019re getting a total gem. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy this ride as much as I have. Come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
